videos.headline: Love sacks King on 3rd down
videos.description: D'Eriq King is brought down for a sack by Mike Love on third down.

videos.headline: King stopped on 4th down
videos.description: Houston goes for it on 4th down and has D'Eriq King brought down for a 3-yard loss.

videos.headline: Johnson pounds in 2-yard TD
videos.description: D'Ernest Johnson runs though the line for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Flowers escapes pass rush, delivers 33-yard pass
videos.description: Quinton Flowers avoids getting sacked and throws a 33-yard pass to Marquez Valdes-Scantling.

videos.headline: Car fumble recovered by USF
videos.description: Mulbah Car coughs up the ball, and it is recovered by Devin Abraham for USF.

videos.headline: Lark snags 39-yard TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King throws a 39-yard touchdown pass to Courtney Lark.

videos.headline: Flowers gives USF the lead
videos.description: Quinton Flowers runs for a touchdown that gives the Bulls a 14-7 lead in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Car punches in game-tying TD
videos.description: After a big run, Mulbah Car punches in a touchdown to even the score at 14.

videos.headline: Car breaks off 46-yard run
videos.description: Mulbah Car's 46-yard run helps set up a game-tying touchdown for Houston.

videos.headline: Flowers runs for his 2nd TD
videos.description: Quinton Flowers scores a go-ahead touchdown on a quarterback sneak.

videos.headline: King runs for 3-yard TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King ties the game at 21 in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Houston hands South Florida its first loss
videos.description: D'Eriq King scrambles and scores a go-ahead touchdown with 11 seconds left to lift Houston to a 28-24 victory.

videos.headline: Houston converts 4th and 24
videos.description: Courtney Lark leaps and snags a 30-yard catch to convert on 4th and long.

videos.headline: King the breakout star in Houston's win
videos.description: Mike Corey and Rene Ingoglia break down Houston's comeback win over South Florida and the big game from quarterback D'Eriq King.

videos.headline: King key to Houston's 28-24 win
videos.description: Rene Ingoglia says that Houston has now found their identity behind new quarterback D'Eriq King.
